data.description: Rare Find! Updated, Move In Ready Ranch with 3 Car Garage Situated on Nearly 5  Acres, Complete with a Peaceful Creek! This Property is THE Perfect Spot for Horse Lovers or Those Looking to Start Their Own Farm. 30 X 40 Barn with a 12 X 14 enclosed lean to. 12 X 45 Carport for Camper Storage. This 2 Bedroom Home Offers the Potential for a 3rd Bedroom with Minimal Effort. Updated Living Room with New Flooring, New Light Fixtures, Accent Wall and Bay Window- Just What Your Plants Have Been Begging For! Kitchen Features Trendy White Cabinets, Wood Flooring and Walk Out to Back Patio. Rain Soft Water Softener/Filtration System, Interior and Exterior Professionally Painted 2021, New Roof Installed 2021, Poured Back Patio Installed 2020. Outdoor Play Set, All Appliances Including Washer and Dryer Stay! Quick and Easy Access to I-75 Without Sacrificing the Peace and Quiet of Country Living!
